Lab - Decreasing Word
This lab was designed to teach you how to use for loops and how to make pretty shapes.

Description
Output a word in a fancy triangle. Use substring to print out smaller sections of the word.

Hints
  for loop i = length-1     down to 0**
    println substrings

Input
hippo
abcd
it
a
chicken

Output
hippo
hipp
hip
hi
h

abcd
abc
ab
a

it
i

a

chicken
chicke
chick
chic
chi
ch
c